## Attention

This package can be used with **Python 3.10+ ONLY**.

## Usage

``` shell
pip3 install yggdrasil-mc
```

``` python
from yggdrasil_mc.client import YggdrasilMC

ygg = YggdrasilMC()
await ygg.by_name_async("SerinaNya")
```

